of magnetic phases in Fe-chalcogenides is an\nimportant material property, since the Fe(Te1-xSex) phase diagram shows\nmagnetism intimately connected with superconductivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 2 Jan 2021 14:27:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
